data.description: Looking for a beautiful and spacious Pool home, located in a great, gated neighborhood, with easy access to shopping and the entire Orlando area and attractions?  This is the place for you!!!!   This home has everything you're looking for in a home.  The Tropical screened pool, with a paver deck, is just off the covered Lanai.  In addition to the lush landscaping, you have an elevated view of the wooded area behind the home.  The living area on the first floor has wood-look plank tile floors.  The huge Kitchen is open to the Great room and a large Breakfast eating area.  There is a Butler's Pantry and a large walk-in Pantry leading to the formal Dining room.  The Kitchen features Stone counters, a huge Island with breakfast bar and Stainless Steel appliances.  The large Primary Suite has a tray ceiling.  The Primary Bathroom features dual Granite topped vanities, large shower, Garden tub, water closet and a generous walk-in closet with direct access to the Laundry.  The upstairs has a spacious Loft area and 3 additional Bedrooms.  One of the Bedrooms has its own Bathroom (Great for guests) and the remaining Bedrooms share the third Bathroom.  Just outside the Guard gate is a Publix shopping center with additional businesses.  The private community activity area with a pool, recreation center, playground and tennis is also conveniently located there.  Mount Dora and all it has to offer is just minutes away.  You have easy access to nearby 429 Western Beltway around Orlando, which gets you to downtown Orlando, The Parks and the airport, as well as the Atlantic coast beaches.  Don't miss the opportunity to own this awesome home!!!
